name: AutoFill
short_description: AutoFill creates profiles that saves your username and password to a secure file that is encrypted with 256x bit encrytion, military grade! Once you hit Submit on the AutoFill program all you have to do is click out on any textbox out side the program and it will input the information! There's also a cancel button unless you change your mind about logging in to something.
summary: AutoFill is a fast password and username entry program.
